# quoted-key-invalid-escape

## Input

```
"bad\z" value

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..14
  ENTRY@0..14
    QUOTED_KEY@0..7
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@0..1 "\""
      STRING@1..6 "bad\\z"
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@6..7 "\""
    SPACE@7..8 " "
    LINE_STRING@8..13
      STRING@8..13 "value"
    NEWLINE@13..14 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: QuotedKey {
                open_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@0..1 "\"",
                string: STRING@1..6 "bad\\z",
                close_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@0..1 "\"",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@8..13 "value",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

